                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yogurtwang/">酸奶</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很实在、很好玩的书，尤其里面写的领袖书单很有价值，当然很多tips不只对领袖有用，need you scoop up, 值得一看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

