              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>共和党人的25本政治必读书单（《领袖必读》）
1 The Seven Fat Years （《富裕的七年》）,by Robert Bartley

2 The Law （《法律》）,by Frederic Bastiat

3 Up from Liberalism （《从自由主义中上升》）,by William F.Buckley,Jr

4 Selected Writings and Speeches of Edmund Burke collected（《埃德蒙·伯克文章与演讲选读》）,by Dr.Peter Stanilis

5 Suicide of the West（《西方的自杀》）,by James Burnham

6 Witness（《见证》）,by Whittaker Chambers

7 Ronald Reagan（《罗纳德·里根》）,by Dinesh D'Souza

8 Advise and Consent（《华府千秋》）,by Allen Drury

9 The Theme is Freedom（《自由的基调》）,by M.Stanton Evans

10 Capitalism and Freedom（《资本主义与自由》）,by Milton Friedman

11 Conscience of a Conservative（《保守派的良知》）,by Barry Goldwater

12 The Road to Serfdom（《通向奴役之路》）,by F.A.Hayek

13 The Fatal Conceit（《致命的自负》）,by F.A.Hayek

14 Economics in One Lession（《经济学概论》）,by Henry Hazlitt

15 Dedication and Leadership（《贡献与领导》）,by Douglas Hyde

16 Modern Times（《现代》）,by Paul Johnson

17 The Conservation Mind（《保守思想》）,by Dr.Russell Kirk

18 The Rise of Radicalism（《极端主义的兴起》）,by Eugene Methvin

19 Defense of Freedom（《为自由辩护》）,by Frank Meyer

20 What is Conservatism（《什么是保守主义》）,by Frank Meyer

21 Atlas Shrugged（《阿特拉斯耸耸肩》）,by Ayn Rand

22 Plunkitt of Tammany Hall（《纽约市民主党机器的运作》）,by William Riordon

23 Knowledge and Decisions（《知识与决定》）,by Thomas Sowell

24 The New Right:We're Ready to Lead（《新一代的右翼：已经做好准备的领袖》）,by Richard Viguerie

25 Ideas Have Consequences（《思想是有结果的》）,by Richard Weaver
</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







