              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                p13 选举日程表：整场选举都是由截止日期来界定的……一个候选人（误了期限）被罚了几次款，就很容易给选民留下无能的印象。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>p24 美国的”党校“：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1）从政的料……不但能说会道，而且很懂得如何与他人交流。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2）训练日程表：过去的历史及现在可能存在的个人问题；从他人的角度看自己；精心打造自己的信息；……<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3）共和党25本必读书单：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>1.The Seven Fat Years, Robert Bartley<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2.The Law,Frederic Bastiat<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>3.Up from Liberalism,William F. Buckley, Jr.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>4.Selected Writings and Speeches of Edmund Burke collected, Dr. Peter Stanilis<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>5.Suicide of the West, James Burham<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>6. Witness, Whittaker Chambers<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>7. Ronald Reagan, Diniesh D' Souza<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>8. Advise and Consent, Allen Drury<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>9. The Theme is Freedom, M. Stanton Evans<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>10. Conscience of a Conservative, Barry Goldwater<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>11.Capitalism and Freedom,  Milton Friedman<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>12. The Road to Serfdom, F.A.Hayek<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>13.The Fatal Conceit, F.A. Hayek<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>14. Economics in One Lesson, Henry Hazlitt<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>15. Dedication and Leadership, Douglas Hyde<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>16. Modern Times, Paul Johnson<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>17. The Conservative Mind, Dr.Russell Krik<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>18. The Rise of Radicalism, Eugene Methvin<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>19. Defense of Freedom, Frank Meyer<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>20. What is Converservation, Frank Meyer<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>21. Atlas Shrugged,Ayn Rand<div style="padding-bottom:1em